Delete a session and garbage-collect its blobs (SRS FR-6.1)

Usage: hh delete [OPTIONS] <SESSION>

Arguments:
  <SESSION>  Session short id, full id, or `last`

Options:
      --yes   Skip the confirmation prompt
  -h, --help  Print help

Example:
  hh delete a1b2c3
  hh delete last --yes
